Anthony Gildès https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anthony_Gild%C3%A8s 0 Anthony Gildès (13 August 1856 – 6 October 1941) was a French actor. Anthony Gildès was born Anatole Gleizes in Metz, France. He died in Paris at age 85. Anthony_Gildès ( 13_August_1856 – 6_October_1941 ) was a_French_actor . Anthony_Gildès was_born Anatole_Gleizes in Metz , France . He died in Paris at age_85 .
